  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "In a large bowl, mix together the sliced almonds, muscovado sugar, and tagine spice blend",
    "Heat the coconut oil in the tagine over medium heat",
    "Add the almond mixture to the tagine and cook for 5 minutes, stirring frequently",
    "Add the water, salt, raisins, and pumpkin seeds to the tagine",
    "Cover the tagine and transfer it to the preheated oven",
    "Bake for 20 minutes, or until the almonds are toasted and fragrant",
    "Remove the tagine from the oven and let it cool for 10 minutes"
  ],
